  "description": "When disaster strikes and upends life in the seaside town of Sweet Haven, Popeye and Wimpy set off on a daring mission to rescue Olive Oyl from the clutches of the villainous Bluto. Toe-tapping tunes, high-seas hijinks, plus a few surprise cameos, Popeye The Musical! is a cartoon come to life—on stage!",
